    "## 3. Check activation shapes\n",
    "\n",
    "Before extracting activations for the whole dataset, make sure I understand what TransformerLens gives me and that the shapes are what I expect.\n",
    "\n",
    "I want: residual stream at each layer, at the *last token position* (since that's what determines the next token — the sycophantic behavior shows up in what token comes next)."
   ]
