    "## 7. Spot-check individual completions against probe predictions\n",
    "\n",
    "I want to understand what the probe is picking up on. Let's look at:\n",
    "- Examples where the probe is confident and correct (what does the model \"know\" that leads to this?)\n",
    "- Examples where the probe is wrong (edge cases, ambiguous labels?)"
   ]
